down(SubnetID,SubnetID).notice: In the path determined by the current subnet id, it moves down in the path from the subnet id given as argument. subnet2 needs to be a prefix of the subnet1. If subnet1 is /a/b/c/d and subnet2 is /a/b, then the returned ID should be /a/b/c.
